---
import PageHeading from "../components/page-heading.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Bangla Web Fonts">
  <section class="relative z-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto my-12 px-7 lg:px-0">
    <PageHeading
      title="Privacy Policy"
      description="Last updated: 15 March 2025"
    />

<p class="mt-4">Welcome to <a href="https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Bangla Web Fonts</a>. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We do not collect personal data from visitors. However, we may collect:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Log Data:</strong> Cloudflare may log IP addresses, browser types, and visit durations for security and performance purposes.</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> Cloudflare Analytics collects anonymous usage data, such as page views and user interactions.</li>
            <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Our site may use cookies to improve functionality and analyze traffic.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Any collected data is used for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Enhancing website performance and security (via Cloudflare)</li>
            <li>Analyzing visitor trends and improving user experience (via Cloudflare Analytics)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We use the following third-party service:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>
                <strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Provides security, content delivery, and analytics services.  
                See Cloudflare's privacy policy <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">here</a>.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">4. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We take reasonable measures to protect your information, but no method is 100% secure.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We may update this policy. Any changes will be posted on this page.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">If you have any questions, please contact us at  
            <a href="https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev/contact" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">our contact page</a>.
        </p>

  </section>
</Layout>